Sentence: The figure confirms that BHO nanorods having a thickness of about 10 nm grow uniformly along the c-axis direction of the SmBCO film.

From the results of the magnetic-field dependence of F p at 77 K, B/c of BHO-doped SmBCO thin film compared to the undoped SmBCO thin film, F p of var- ious amounts of BHO-doped SmBCO thin films improved significantly throughout the entire magnetic field.
